member.remarks:
Below is the JSON schema for the response payload.
Response Body:
Schema for GetLanguagesResult: { translation: Dictionary<string, TranslationLanguage>, # Required. Languages that support translate API. transliteration: Dictionary<string, TransliterationLanguage>, # Required. Languages that support transliteration API. dictionary: Dictionary<string, SourceDictionaryLanguage>, # Required. Languages that support dictionary API. }

